  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要一个桑基图来展示公司收入的流向分配。总收入进来之后，要拆到五个去处：工资、运营、市场、研发，最后剩下的才是利润。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Revenue",
        "Salaries",
        "Operations",
        "Marketing",
        "R&D",
        "Profit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我想确认一下比例：工资占40%，运营25%，市场15%，研发12%，利润8%——这样加起来是100%吗？40加25是65，加15到80，加12到92，最后利润8刚好凑满。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Revenue",
        "Salaries",
        "Operations",
        "Marketing",
        "R&D",
        "Profit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个比例。利润8%确实偏低，但这就是现状，先如实呈现。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Profit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经用sankey-beta格式把图画出来了。Revenue作为唯一源头，五条带分别流向五个节点，宽度按百分比自动渲染。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Revenue",
        "Salaries",
        "Operations",
        "Marketing",
        "R&D",
        "Profit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "稍等，我注意到一个问题——R&D的投入只有12%，但我们的战略是技术驱动，这个数值会不会在视觉上显得研发被边缘化了？要不要调整一下标签顺序，把R&D放在运营前面，让它更醒目？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R&D",
        "Operations"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "桑基图的节点顺序我可以调整，但流量比例是固定的。您希望把R&D节点排在Marketing之后、Operations之前，还是整体重新排序？目前是按金额从大到小排的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R&D",
        "Operations",
        "Marketing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不用改顺序了，按金额大小排更客观。我刚才的顾虑不对——故意把小额条目往前调反而会误导读者。保持原样：Salaries 40、Operations 25、Marketing 15、R&D 12、Profit 8。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Salaries",
        "Operations",
        "Marketing",
        "R&D",
        "Profit"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认最终版本：Revenue单一源头，五路分流，标签和比例不变，节点按数值降序排列。图表已就绪。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Revenue",
